        {
          "anchor" : "Swift-Testing",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Swift Testing",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The new ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/testing",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " library is the recommended way",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "to write tests for your Wasm projects. All of its cross-platform APIs are available on WebAssembly, providing a modern and expressive way to validate your code.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "XCTest",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "XCTest",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "identifier" : "https:\/\/github.com\/swiftlang\/swift-corelibs-xctest",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " is available",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "on WebAssembly platforms, and you can use it to write tests for your Wasm projects.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The following XCTest features are unavailable when targeting Wasm:",
